layers.name: LDW City Boundaries
layers.description: Combined incorporated city limit boundaries and unincorporated Urban Growth Areas (UGA) as defined by the Growth Management Act. Updates made in 2019 were made by collecting city limits and urban growth area boundary infomation from each of Washington's 39 counties, where available, and the Washington State Department of Transportation.
layers.copyrightText: Washington State Counties, Washington State Department of Ecology, Office of the Chief Information Officer-Geospatial Program Office, Washington State Department of Transportation
